{{flavour|Summons one or more air elementals.}}

'''Summon Air Elementals''' is a monster-only spell which summons hostile [[air elemental]]s into existence. These can be incredibly dangerous, with their semi-irresistible [[Stunning Burst]] spell able to briefly paralyse the player. Fighting in corridors is advisable against monsters with this spell.

{{monsters with spell}}

Sojobo can sustain at most three elementals summoned by this spell.

